title: Shannon and the Clams - Do I Wanna Stay (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Shannon and the Clams performing “Do I Wanna Stay” live in the KEXP studio. Recorded March 18, 2022.

Shannon Shaw - Bass / Vocals
